==English==
===Etymology===
From the French verb [[oublier]], to [[forget]]; from the Middle French; from the Vulgar Latin ''[[oblivisci]].'' Recognized as English in 1819.
===Noun===
'''oubliette'''
# [[Dungeon]] only accessible by a [[trapdoor]] at the top.

